divs: Sighting DetailsMy wife and I were driving south on rt19 toward Washington, PA when I noticed the lights at first I thought they were plane's, We pulled into aldi's parking lot my wife went in to buy some things I stayed in the car watching the lights they were not moving, you could see small plane's flying what looked like below the object's in the driection of the Washington Co. airport. When my wife came back to the car I showed her the lights were still there, she didn't know what to think but she wasn't convinced (she doesn't believe in UFO's). We went to eat-n-park after dinner we went to walmart same location as where I was watching the light's and they weren't there,there wasn't any more cloud cover these light's just weren't there. Do you have any other report's? Feel free to contact me if you need to by cell phone.
